Package: spopt
Title: Spatial Optimization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kyle", "Walker", , "kyle@walker-data.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("PySAL Developers", role = "cph",
           comment = "Original Python spopt library")
  )
Description: Spatial optimization algorithms for regionalization and facility
    location problems. Includes algorithms for spatial clustering (Max-P,
    AZP, SKATER, SPENC, Ward) and optimal facility siting (P-Median, P-Center,
    MCLP, LSCP, P-Dispersion, FRLM). Uses a Rust backend via extendr for
    performance and the HiGHS solver for mixed-integer programming.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
